# Scenes

Scene management for game flow and state transitions.

## Files to Create

- **SceneManager.lua** - Central scene manager
- **MenuScene.lua** - Main menu scene
- **GameScene.lua** - Main gameplay scene
- **PauseScene.lua** - Pause menu overlay
- **GameOverScene.lua** - Game over screen
- **VictoryScene.lua** - Victory screen
- **OptionsScene.lua** - Settings/options menu

Ask @gameflow to implement the scene management system!
